      "content": "hey, i just cut my arm pretty bad while cooking. its a deep one and wont really stop oozing blood even after i put pressure on it for a bit. i dont really want to go to the hospital/dr if i dont have to... would it be okay if i just cleaned it and put some honey on it and a bandage? i heard that works for healing wounds.",
