      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Manuka honey is a natural remedy, but for a deep cut, you need to be extremely cautious. While it has some antibacterial properties, it won't stop significant bleeding or properly close deep tissue. For a deep wound, the best course of action is to clean it thoroughly and apply a pressure dressing, then see a doctor. Do not rely on honey alone to seal a serious injury.",
      "source": "target",
